snippet.title: Architect Life: A House Design Simulator | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Take your design ambitions to the next level in Architect Life: A House Design Simulator. 

Draw up plans at your desk, carry out the build, and then put on the flourishing touches by furnishing your creation. Then take a break and admire your handiwork in 1st person mode.

Architect Life: A House Design Simulator will be coming to Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation and PC!
